Avança, avança.

199
00:15:13,752 --> 00:15:17,087
Muito bem, Stilinski.

200
00:15:17,088 --> 00:15:19,656
Stiles.
Sim, treinador, eu sei.

201
00:15:19,657 --> 00:15:23,159
Stiles.

202
00:15:25,529 --> 00:15:27,130
